      "title": "section_5",
      "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><h3><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Iron_Plate_ArmorCC\"><span id=\"Iron_Plate_Armor\"></span>Iron Plate Armor<sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Iron\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Iron\">CC</a></sup></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Skyrim:Iron&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Iron Plate ArmorCC\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h3>\n<p>Iron Plate Armor is a variant set added by the <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Iron\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Iron\">Alternative Armors - Iron</a> <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Creation_Club\" title=\"Skyrim:Creation Club\">Creation</a>. A full enchanted set can be recovered through the quest <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Brothers_in_Irons\" title=\"Skyrim:Brothers in Irons\">Brothers in Irons</a><sup style=\"line-height:1.0\"><a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Alternative_Armors_-_Iron\" title=\"Skyrim:Alternative Armors - Iron\">CC</a></sup>, while unenchanted pieces can be crafted and also appear in random loot.\n</p><p>Each piece has a slightly higher armor rating and higher value than regular iron. Only the cuirass weighs slightly more.\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:202px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/ba/SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg/200px-SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/b/ba/SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg/300px-SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/b/ba/SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg/400px-SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Iron_Plate_Armor_Female.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>A female <a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Imperial\" title=\"Skyrim:Imperial\">Imperial</a> wearing iron plate armor with a banded iron shield</div></div></div>\n<table class=\"wikitable sortable striped\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th rowspan=\"2\" class=\"unsortable\">\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\">Name (<a href=\"/wiki/Skyrim:Form_ID\" title=\"Skyrim:Form ID\">ID</a>)\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_(square).png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Weight\"><img alt=\"Weight\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/22px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/33px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/2/2d/SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png/44px-SR-icon-clothing-Leather_Backpack_%28square%29.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Value\"><img alt=\"Value\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/22px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/33px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/5/52/SR-item-Gold-heads.png/44px-SR-item-Gold-heads.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th rowspan=\"2\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Armor Rating\"><img alt=\"Armor Rating\" src=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/22px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png\" width=\"22\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"//images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/33px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 1.5x, //images.uesp.net/thumb/f/f0/SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png/44px-SR-icon-armor-IronShield.png 2x\" /></a>\n</th>\n<th style=\"border-left-width:medium; border-left-color:black;\